WEBVTT

02:21.240 --> 02:22.320
What a pity.

02:25.160 --> 02:27.080
We were this close to finding the answer.

02:30.680 --> 02:33.560
The prayer ceremony begins now.

02:36.120 --> 02:39.560
Isn't the prayer ceremony supposed
to be held two days before the wedding?

02:39.640 --> 02:40.760
Besides,

02:41.560 --> 02:43.440
I've already stolen the Radiant Moon.

02:45.120 --> 02:46.680
What's going on?

02:48.440 --> 02:51.440
People always say
that the past can't be changed

02:52.280 --> 02:53.400
and that years flow like water.

02:54.640 --> 02:57.720
This is the first time
I've felt it so vividly.

02:58.800 --> 02:59.960
Humans

03:00.040 --> 03:01.680
and demons alike,

03:01.760 --> 03:03.240
even the Dragon Deity himself,

03:03.880 --> 03:07.480
are so small before fate.

03:08.320 --> 03:12.120
Inside the Star Stone
is an illusion of the past.

03:12.200 --> 03:13.840
Since it's the past,

03:13.920 --> 03:16.480
it cannot be reversed or changed.

03:17.120 --> 03:19.840
The moment something
that could alter the past happens,

03:20.440 --> 03:22.440
the illusion will shift and leap,

03:23.040 --> 03:25.840
correcting itself automatically
to erase the traces of error

03:27.560 --> 03:28.880
and move on to the next

03:29.600 --> 03:31.560
destined moment that cannot be changed.

03:49.880 --> 03:52.000
You keep looking at me
without saying anything.

03:52.520 --> 03:53.440
What do you want?

03:55.840 --> 03:56.920
If you'd known

03:57.760 --> 03:59.480
you couldn't use demon magic just now,

04:03.240 --> 04:05.480
would you still have stepped
in front of me without hesitation?

04:09.320 --> 04:11.840
Of course not. I'm not stupid.

04:37.880 --> 04:38.880
What are you looking at?

04:40.880 --> 04:41.800
The moon.

04:45.600 --> 04:46.640
Don't be ridiculous.

04:47.440 --> 04:50.040
The sky is pitch-black. Where's the moon?

04:51.080 --> 04:52.120
It's there.

04:53.320 --> 04:54.560
It's called <i>Hui</i>.

05:00.040 --> 05:03.040
I've heard
that everyone in the Formless Moon

05:03.120 --> 05:04.560
has a mark on their arm.

05:05.400 --> 05:06.560
Why don't you have one?

05:08.440 --> 05:11.640
Because my moon phase is <i>Hui</i>.

05:12.600 --> 05:13.560
<i>Hui</i>?

05:13.640 --> 05:16.440
<i>When you can't see the moon at night,</i>

05:16.520 --> 05:17.960
<i>that moon phase</i>

05:18.600 --> 05:19.640
<i>is Hui.</i>

05:21.480 --> 05:22.600
You said

05:23.360 --> 05:25.040
that even if you were shattered to pieces,

05:25.120 --> 05:26.280
you could still be reborn.

05:27.440 --> 05:28.680
But will the reborn you

05:30.800 --> 05:31.840
still be the original you?

05:34.240 --> 05:36.680
The Primordial Sacred Spring can share

05:36.760 --> 05:38.040
and preserve memories.

05:38.640 --> 05:40.880
We are all reborn with memories.

05:40.960 --> 05:42.200
That's incredible.

05:44.200 --> 05:45.360
What does it feel like

05:47.120 --> 05:48.720
to share memories with others?

05:51.800 --> 05:53.120
It's hard to explain.

05:55.200 --> 05:56.200
Is it really?

06:00.160 --> 06:03.560
The Golden Scale Tree in the Shilin Sect
has always had a special fragrance.

06:03.640 --> 06:05.520
-You know that, right?
-Of course.

06:06.760 --> 06:09.120
Then how would you describe
that scent to someone

06:09.200 --> 06:10.600
who's never been to the Shilin Sect?

06:15.760 --> 06:16.800
I think

06:18.640 --> 06:19.880
I understand what you mean now.

06:21.120 --> 06:22.360
Take

06:23.360 --> 06:26.160
the special scent you carry for example.

06:26.240 --> 06:27.720
I can't describe what it's like either.

06:28.400 --> 06:30.280
You've described it plenty of times,

06:30.960 --> 06:33.840
comparing it
to wildflowers in a mountain valley

06:33.920 --> 06:35.480
and heavy snow at an ancient temple.

06:38.680 --> 06:40.240
Do I really carry a scent?

06:41.920 --> 06:44.640
You do. You always think I'm lying to you.

06:48.160 --> 06:49.800
Maybe it's just my natural scent.

06:58.320 --> 06:59.800
There's no new moon in the sky,

07:00.800 --> 07:02.560
just like I didn't exist
in the Formless Moon either

07:03.600 --> 07:04.640
<i>at the very start.</i>

07:05.880 --> 07:07.400
<i>When I was first born,</i>

07:08.760 --> 07:09.920
<i>I always dreamed</i>

07:11.320 --> 07:13.960
<i>that my sisters couldn't see me</i>

07:14.640 --> 07:16.040
<i>when I was with them.</i>

08:06.160 --> 08:07.200
Wangyan,

08:08.000 --> 08:09.080
thank you.

08:12.360 --> 08:14.200
You're the only one who can see me.

08:14.800 --> 08:16.760
You always hide in the dark.

08:17.360 --> 08:19.400
Of course, the others
can't see you easily.

08:21.520 --> 08:22.600
But I can.

08:23.400 --> 08:24.760
My heart

08:25.920 --> 08:27.720
can feel where you are.

08:29.600 --> 08:30.800
<i>Later,</i>

08:30.880 --> 08:33.000
<i>Wangyan always took me</i>
<i>with her wherever she went.</i>

08:33.840 --> 08:35.799
And I never had those lonely dreams again.

08:37.799 --> 08:39.480
Though the new moon exists,

08:40.200 --> 08:41.880
barely anyone can see it.

08:44.640 --> 08:46.240
Only those who care about it

08:46.840 --> 08:48.480
will keep looking up

08:49.920 --> 08:52.200
and search for it in all that darkness.

08:55.840 --> 08:56.960
I can see it.

08:59.640 --> 09:01.600
Whether it's the waxing and waning moon

09:02.720 --> 09:04.200
or the stars spread across the sky,

09:05.400 --> 09:07.000
they all have their own orbits.

09:08.840 --> 09:09.880
No place

09:11.080 --> 09:12.440
can ever replace another.

09:18.200 --> 09:21.040
You're the Dragon Deity.
Of course you wouldn't understand.

09:22.680 --> 09:24.320
But even the Dragon Deity will fall.

09:24.400 --> 09:26.240
My eight elder brothers

09:27.040 --> 09:28.640
are all gone.

09:29.760 --> 09:30.800
And one day,

09:31.720 --> 09:32.760
I will

09:34.600 --> 09:36.560
step down from this divine throne too.

09:39.840 --> 09:41.080
Are you afraid

09:42.760 --> 09:44.240
of falling,

09:45.800 --> 09:48.440
of no longer being a deity revered by all?

10:19.720 --> 10:20.760
Who would've thought?

10:22.240 --> 10:23.320
The stone we've been searching for

10:24.800 --> 10:26.160
is actually a person.

10:30.040 --> 10:33.360
But didn't the Star Stone shatter
in that Meteor Blast long ago?

10:35.720 --> 10:36.760
Master Chi Wen,

10:38.320 --> 10:39.800
the Dragon Deity, saved me.

10:48.440 --> 10:50.480
I am disaster itself.

10:51.600 --> 10:53.160
I am the abyss.

10:55.040 --> 10:56.840
Why did you save me?

10:57.840 --> 11:01.200
If all it takes is one pebble falling
to break the silence,

11:02.720 --> 11:04.200
then it is no longer an abyss.

11:06.280 --> 11:08.720
You bear extraordinary power
from beyond the heavens.

11:08.800 --> 11:11.640
Slaughter is not your only choice.

11:13.000 --> 11:14.800
Now that your chains are gone,

11:14.880 --> 11:16.200
you are free.

11:16.280 --> 11:18.160
So is your will.

11:18.240 --> 11:20.760
It is up to you to choose

11:21.360 --> 11:22.840
between slaughter and protection.

11:24.320 --> 11:25.800
I hope that one day,

11:25.880 --> 11:28.520
you'll find the true meaning
of coming to this world

11:28.600 --> 11:31.560
after crossing countless galaxies.

11:32.520 --> 11:34.520
Master Chi Wen even gave me a dragon fang

11:35.520 --> 11:37.600
and taught me how to control my power.

11:38.280 --> 11:40.800
But in the end, countless lives
were still lost because of me.

11:41.600 --> 11:42.800
I couldn't forgive myself.

11:43.400 --> 11:44.880
After that,

11:44.960 --> 11:47.640
I became a monk and shaved my head.

11:48.240 --> 11:50.600
From that day on, there was
no more Star Stone and no more Tian Di.

11:51.560 --> 11:54.800
Later, I wandered the mortal world,
punishing the wicked.

11:55.400 --> 11:57.760
And before I knew it,
I had earned myself a new fearsome name.

11:59.360 --> 12:01.000
No wonder people say

12:01.080 --> 12:02.880
you returned to worldly life,
fell into demonhood,

12:02.960 --> 12:05.240
and became the demon monk

12:05.320 --> 12:06.840
known as Xie Lingxi.

12:08.200 --> 12:11.080
I was a demon to begin with.
How could I "fall into demonhood"?

12:11.880 --> 12:13.400
I had no name in the first place.

12:13.480 --> 12:15.280
It makes little difference

12:16.560 --> 12:17.600
what the world calls me.

12:18.200 --> 12:20.200
But why did you come back here?

12:20.760 --> 12:22.960
Why do you refuse to help Wu Zhiqi

12:23.040 --> 12:25.480
lift the Petrification Curse
from the Green Ape clan?

12:26.360 --> 12:27.680
You're tormenting him

12:29.360 --> 12:30.880
to take revenge on him, aren't you?

12:36.000 --> 12:37.920
I've never resented him.

12:39.560 --> 12:40.640
Why would I want revenge?

12:43.080 --> 12:44.240
I came back

12:44.320 --> 12:46.960
because of a promise
I once made to Chi Wen.

12:48.240 --> 12:49.280
I promised him

12:52.320 --> 12:53.960
I would protect someone for him.

13:00.040 --> 13:01.080
So,

13:03.960 --> 13:05.760
I've hated the wrong person all along.

13:06.400 --> 13:09.960
The slaughter of the flood dragon clan
wasn't Shilin Sect or Chi Wen's doing.

13:32.320 --> 13:33.160
Iced lotus seeds?

13:34.600 --> 13:35.840
You can use demon magic again?

13:38.280 --> 13:41.040
I made them in my room
after the prayer ceremony.

13:42.520 --> 13:43.920
When I was little,

13:44.000 --> 13:46.040
Wangyan used to make them
for me all the time.

13:46.120 --> 13:47.240
They're crisp and refreshing.

13:50.960 --> 13:52.000
It feels

13:54.120 --> 13:55.920
like I've been apart from Wangyan forever.

14:00.240 --> 14:01.600
Go on. Try them.

14:01.680 --> 14:03.840
Once you've finished,
we'll go get the Star Stone

14:03.920 --> 14:04.760
and get out of here.

14:12.640 --> 14:13.880
I forgot.

14:13.960 --> 14:17.640
Master Chi Wen
never eats what others give him.

14:19.040 --> 14:20.560
I shouldn't have bothered.

14:40.000 --> 14:41.840
Sometimes I think

14:42.560 --> 14:44.680
about the real Di Zhu
from over 1,000 years ago.

14:48.120 --> 14:49.160
Do you think

14:50.400 --> 14:51.600
she was foolish?

14:54.240 --> 14:58.880
People often say that love is a gamble
and that the heart is the stake.

15:01.600 --> 15:05.000
But some people
will wager everything they have,

15:06.040 --> 15:07.600
even when they're battered and bruised.

15:10.720 --> 15:12.440
But Di Zhu lost that gamble.

15:12.520 --> 15:15.520
In the legend, Man Man was a killer.

15:17.000 --> 15:18.120
But I think

15:19.160 --> 15:22.200
Man Man truly loved Di Zhu.

15:25.360 --> 15:26.920
Whether he did or not,

15:27.880 --> 15:29.680
Man Man still deceived Di Zhu.

15:31.680 --> 15:32.880
And I

15:34.240 --> 15:35.720
hate deception more than anything.

15:38.960 --> 15:41.760
Are you implying something?

15:52.960 --> 15:54.080
You…

16:31.200 --> 16:32.640
In the end, I still can't

16:33.680 --> 16:35.960
leave this Star Stone illusion, can I?

16:37.640 --> 16:38.760
A Star Stone illusion?

16:41.960 --> 16:43.040
You mean

16:44.560 --> 16:46.400
this is an illusion created by me?

16:54.680 --> 16:55.840
I understand now.

16:58.360 --> 16:59.480
In this illusion,

17:00.280 --> 17:02.480
there is a truth
that you don't want him to know.

17:03.040 --> 17:05.000
So you want to kill the Star Stone

17:05.760 --> 17:07.040
and see whether that
can break the illusion.

17:07.119 --> 17:10.240
My hands are already stained with blood.

17:12.319 --> 17:14.280
A little more won't matter.

17:18.480 --> 17:19.599
My weak point

17:20.359 --> 17:22.720
lies one cun below my left collarbone.

17:25.040 --> 17:26.880
Go on. Strike here.

17:32.040 --> 17:33.320
Why?

17:35.520 --> 17:36.400
Child,

17:37.400 --> 17:38.920
the shackles in your heart

17:40.080 --> 17:42.240
were not forged from your sins.

17:43.520 --> 17:44.560
Your heart

17:45.200 --> 17:47.440
has lost its way
under pressure and self-torment.

17:48.280 --> 17:49.960
That's why I cannot see your heart.

17:51.480 --> 17:53.520
I'm willing to help free you
from this sea of suffering.

17:54.760 --> 17:56.240
The splendor in a dream

17:57.400 --> 17:58.680
is, after all, illusory.

18:09.480 --> 18:11.000
Only when the dream ends

18:12.080 --> 18:13.400
does the truth appear.

18:16.640 --> 18:18.000
But the truth

18:19.440 --> 18:20.440
is too bitter.

18:27.440 --> 18:29.640
For the past millennium,
I've been asking myself

18:31.760 --> 18:34.080
why I came into this world

18:36.320 --> 18:37.360
and what

18:39.400 --> 18:41.320
I could do for it.

18:56.560 --> 18:59.320
Master Chi Wen, you're finally awake.

19:00.640 --> 19:03.800
You were so well-behaved
while you were asleep.

19:10.080 --> 19:11.880
You poisoned the iced lotus seeds?

19:13.880 --> 19:16.200
Don't make it sound so bad.
It was only a sleeping draught.

19:17.360 --> 19:18.400
Still,

19:19.200 --> 19:23.520
getting you to lower your guard
and obediently eat food from someone else

19:23.600 --> 19:25.120
was truly difficult.

19:25.200 --> 19:27.280
A fox really can't be trusted.

19:28.520 --> 19:29.840
What exactly are you trying to do?

19:32.280 --> 19:34.080
How can you sound so self-righteous

19:34.880 --> 19:36.680
when you were the one
who played tricks first?

19:38.120 --> 19:39.440
Tell me.

19:39.520 --> 19:41.520
Why did you pour out
the realgar powder from my sachet?

19:41.600 --> 19:43.600
Why are you dawdling? Come in.

19:44.440 --> 19:45.400
I'm coming.

19:56.000 --> 19:57.320
Are you that reluctant to leave?

19:59.280 --> 20:02.840
Don't tell me you really
want to stay and marry me.

20:03.800 --> 20:05.040
Don't flatter yourself.

20:06.400 --> 20:08.440
I just want to catch the killer.

20:10.360 --> 20:12.320
Then I'm even more baffled.

20:12.400 --> 20:13.480
What's the point?

20:14.400 --> 20:17.840
This is an illusion of the past.
None of this has anything to do with us.

20:18.440 --> 20:21.640
What happened in the past
can't be undone or changed.

20:22.240 --> 20:23.200
So why go to all this extra trouble?

20:24.000 --> 20:25.320
Don't you think it's suspicious?

20:26.080 --> 20:28.640
A demon that can possess people
and control them at will

20:29.240 --> 20:31.800
has always been exceedingly rare.

20:32.400 --> 20:34.920
Doesn't that remind you of anyone?

20:38.840 --> 20:40.040
Jiu Ying?

20:48.120 --> 20:49.840
You know the Star Stone
better than anyone.

20:50.640 --> 20:53.520
Do the illusions inside it
belong to anyone?

20:54.240 --> 20:57.760
Like dreams, whose memories
are these illusions of the past

20:58.480 --> 20:59.960
they've entered?

21:00.960 --> 21:03.520
Among those who've entered
the same illusion,

21:03.600 --> 21:07.200
one of them
is the master of that illusion.

21:07.960 --> 21:10.360
It is a past they once lived through.

21:11.880 --> 21:13.600
But the wonder of the Star Stone

21:14.800 --> 21:16.440
is that the master's consciousness

21:17.320 --> 21:19.160
enters someone else's body

21:20.760 --> 21:22.760
to relive it all

21:24.000 --> 21:25.520
as an observer.

21:26.960 --> 21:28.160
That way,

21:28.240 --> 21:31.120
the things that have
confused them for years

21:31.720 --> 21:33.920
can finally make sense when seen

21:34.520 --> 21:35.560
through an outsider's eyes.

21:36.280 --> 21:37.640
Take Wu Shiguang.

21:37.720 --> 21:42.080
He traveled to his own childhood.

21:42.160 --> 21:44.640
But he's reliving it

21:45.240 --> 21:47.120
through his father Cang Hao's perspective.

21:47.720 --> 21:48.960
So Wu Shiguang wants to find

21:49.840 --> 21:52.280
the truth behind the destruction
of the flood dragon clan?

21:52.360 --> 21:53.400
No.

21:53.920 --> 21:55.880
It's the Star Stone that wants them
to know the answers.

21:57.000 --> 21:59.600
-The Star Stone?
-Didn't you see it too?

22:00.480 --> 22:01.800
It's Xie Lingxi.

22:02.880 --> 22:05.960
But the world Master Chi Wen
and Lu Wuyi entered

22:06.040 --> 22:07.360
was from 1,000 years ago.

22:08.120 --> 22:10.240
It has nothing to do with either of them.

22:11.040 --> 22:12.800
Who is the master

22:14.800 --> 22:15.840
of that illusion?

22:17.360 --> 22:18.400
Bai Ze,

22:20.080 --> 22:21.600
why don't you ask me

22:22.680 --> 22:24.200
who the master is

22:24.960 --> 22:26.200
in Li Jie's illusion?

22:27.720 --> 22:29.120
So you do know.

22:30.200 --> 22:33.080
Who would've thought that Master Bai Ze,
who knows everything under heaven,

22:34.120 --> 22:35.160
would have secrets too?

22:36.240 --> 22:37.440
Yuan Wuhuo.

22:39.000 --> 22:40.200
Yuan Xizai.

22:44.640 --> 22:45.600
How interesting.

22:49.320 --> 22:51.280
How did you find out
where the Star Stone was hidden?

22:52.360 --> 22:54.560
Are there any other spies
among the Green Ape clan?

22:55.560 --> 22:56.600
Report!

22:57.360 --> 22:59.600
Master Wu Zhiqi,
Master Six-Eyed Butterfly has arrived.

22:59.680 --> 23:01.840
-He's here to take the Star Stone.
-All right.

23:04.880 --> 23:06.800
This cage, like the chains on Tian Di,

23:07.920 --> 23:09.880
is made of tough spirit sand.

23:10.520 --> 23:13.240
Only the hardest obsidian can break it.

23:18.280 --> 23:19.360
You can't escape.

23:20.760 --> 23:24.160
And don't even think
about taking Tian Di with you.

23:34.680 --> 23:37.160
You really shouldn't
be trapped here by me.

23:38.640 --> 23:39.800
The world is vast,

23:41.160 --> 23:42.320
but it is cruel too.

23:43.840 --> 23:46.840
You can resent me or hate me,

23:48.080 --> 23:50.040
but some roads

23:53.560 --> 23:55.200
were destined for you and me all along.

24:17.320 --> 24:18.360
Don't be sad.

24:19.560 --> 24:20.840
He wants to let you go.

24:22.520 --> 24:25.080
Fortunately, the birthday gift
my little brother gave me years ago

24:26.080 --> 24:27.280
was obsidian.

24:31.080 --> 24:33.520
Only the hardest obsidian

24:34.440 --> 24:35.640
can break it.

24:36.360 --> 24:37.560
Wu Zhiqi

24:39.000 --> 24:41.320
was reminding us on purpose.

25:08.280 --> 25:09.360
Good for you, Man Man.

25:10.280 --> 25:11.640
You knew where the Star Stone was

25:11.720 --> 25:13.360
and didn't tell me?

25:13.440 --> 25:15.400
The Star Stone isn't yours.

25:15.480 --> 25:16.760
Why should he tell you?

25:17.520 --> 25:20.320
You look human enough. Have you no shame?

25:22.320 --> 25:24.360
I knew something was off with you.

25:25.520 --> 25:26.600
Turns out you really did betray me.

25:27.440 --> 25:29.760
This woman is clearly pure trouble.

25:30.360 --> 25:31.200
A vixen through and through.

25:33.320 --> 25:34.440
Then, do you know

25:35.000 --> 25:37.280
that foxes never forget a grudge?

25:37.880 --> 25:40.520
I still haven't settled the score
for you killing me.

25:41.520 --> 25:42.760
Killing you?

25:43.360 --> 25:44.440
What do you mean, killing you?

25:45.040 --> 25:46.720
I'll kill you now!

26:13.480 --> 26:14.520
You…

26:16.200 --> 26:17.360
You're only human.

26:18.520 --> 26:19.640
Why are you immune to my magic?

26:26.600 --> 26:27.680
Looks like Lu Wuyi

26:27.760 --> 26:29.960
is even more formidable than we thought.

26:30.040 --> 26:32.760
Bai Ze, you know
the secrets of all demons.

26:34.200 --> 26:35.840
What kind of power is this?

26:36.640 --> 26:39.200
The more she's attacked
by the same kind of magic,

26:39.280 --> 26:42.160
the more she's able to absorb
its power and grow immune to it.

26:51.120 --> 26:53.080
I've been away from the world too long.

26:54.040 --> 26:57.320
When did the people
of the Formless Moon become this powerful?

26:58.920 --> 27:00.840
-Be careful.
-What are you scared of?

27:03.040 --> 27:04.600
You killed me last time.

27:05.480 --> 27:08.280
Now it's time you paid back that life.

27:09.040 --> 27:10.440
What nonsense.

27:11.480 --> 27:13.120
I have no idea what you're talking about.

27:15.160 --> 27:17.080
-Hand over the Star Stone.
-Don't act rashly.

27:17.160 --> 27:18.640
Give me the Star Stone,

27:19.520 --> 27:20.840
or I'll kill her right now.

27:20.920 --> 27:22.480
I was telling her not to act rashly.

27:26.520 --> 27:28.320
Kneel and obey me.

27:34.760 --> 27:36.440
Don't kill him.
The illusion will go haywire!

28:17.280 --> 28:21.400
THE DAY OF THE HURRICANE CATASTROPHE

28:22.400 --> 28:23.680
I'll cut his chains.

28:23.760 --> 28:26.360
You go outside the cave first
and see if there are any Green Ape guards.

28:26.440 --> 28:27.520
All right.

29:26.520 --> 29:28.520
AN HOUR BEFORE THE METEOR BLAST

29:30.640 --> 29:34.160
A moth will fly into the flame,

29:34.760 --> 29:36.400
even knowing it's wrong.

29:37.280 --> 29:40.680
I am no different.

29:57.360 --> 29:58.400
Master!

30:02.560 --> 30:03.720
Why?

30:10.080 --> 30:11.600
All things flourish and fade
in their time.

30:12.840 --> 30:14.400
Life and death are nothing strange.

30:19.080 --> 30:20.560
I had hoped to see you through this,

30:22.080 --> 30:23.120
but it seems…

30:32.040 --> 30:33.080
Master…

30:34.040 --> 30:35.120
Master!

31:06.200 --> 31:11.240
THE DAY OF THE GREAT FREEZE

31:15.760 --> 31:17.520
What happened?

31:19.560 --> 31:21.320
The illusion seems
to be jumping on its own.

31:22.840 --> 31:24.480
It's correcting itself automatically.

31:32.280 --> 31:33.800
Move that one over there.

31:33.880 --> 31:35.440
Time's jumped that far ahead?

31:47.360 --> 31:48.440
Di Zhu,

31:48.520 --> 31:50.040
here's the Star Stone!

31:51.720 --> 31:52.560
‎What?

31:53.600 --> 31:54.480
That's easy.

32:06.440 --> 32:07.680
What's going on?

32:10.040 --> 32:11.080
How did everything suddenly change?

32:14.160 --> 32:15.000
I don't know either.

32:22.720 --> 32:24.280
You're finally here.

32:31.960 --> 32:34.640
You've done well
with the task we assigned you.

32:34.720 --> 32:36.520
Hand him over.
I'll take him back to the Shilin Sect.

32:39.640 --> 32:41.840
The Shilin Sect
will take good care of you.

32:42.560 --> 32:44.000
I'll go see you later.

32:54.200 --> 32:55.360
What are you doing?

32:56.240 --> 32:58.120
There's something hidden inside you.

32:58.200 --> 32:59.240
I'll help you take it out.

33:12.440 --> 33:14.080
Wu Shiguang is in my hands now.

33:16.640 --> 33:17.840
So it really was him.

33:22.640 --> 33:24.640
If you want him safe,

33:25.320 --> 33:27.440
lift the Petrification Curse
from my clansmen.

33:35.960 --> 33:37.040
Master…

33:52.360 --> 33:54.040
Shiguang always calls you Master,

33:55.400 --> 33:56.600
but in his heart,

34:02.360 --> 34:04.200
he's always seen you as family.

34:07.160 --> 34:08.400
You're no child anymore.

34:09.800 --> 34:12.080
Why are you suddenly crying like one?

34:15.239 --> 34:16.159
Don't worry.

34:17.400 --> 34:18.920
I'll get Shiguang out.

36:09.160 --> 36:11.600
So Master went to save me.

36:13.040 --> 36:15.600
If he hadn't gone with Wu Zhiqi that day,

36:18.240 --> 36:19.520
would everything have been different?

36:25.920 --> 36:26.960
Today

36:29.120 --> 36:30.720
is the day the flood dragon clan

36:32.520 --> 36:34.040
is wiped out.

36:48.160 --> 36:50.320
They're getting married!

36:51.040 --> 36:52.560
They're getting married!

36:54.360 --> 36:55.400
They're getting married!

36:56.800 --> 36:58.240
They're getting married!

37:04.280 --> 37:07.120
-So this isn't a dream.
-Why didn't you pinch yourself?

37:07.200 --> 37:09.280
-Because I'm not stupid.
-I…

37:11.680 --> 37:17.200
You know, that wedding robe looks good
on you, Master Dragon Deity.

37:21.040 --> 37:23.360
A true dragon looks good in anything.

37:23.440 --> 37:24.720
No need to be surprised.

37:28.600 --> 37:33.040
A Dragon Deity above mortal concerns
is suddenly decked out in gold and silver,

37:33.120 --> 37:34.040
about to wed.

37:34.120 --> 37:35.720
How's that not surprising?

37:40.000 --> 37:42.360
By the way, Master Dragon Deity,

37:42.440 --> 37:45.600
do you have any experience
with the wedding night?

37:47.320 --> 37:49.240
Nothing unexpected will happen, right?

37:54.200 --> 37:55.240
Wait for me.

37:55.960 --> 37:57.000
Just wait here.

38:09.040 --> 38:11.640
I'm not getting jilted, am I?

38:30.720 --> 38:31.760
What is it?

38:33.640 --> 38:34.680
Something good.

38:58.560 --> 38:59.600
Trust me.

39:00.800 --> 39:02.840
This guarantees nothing can go wrong.

39:10.120 --> 39:11.160
Why are you smiling?

39:12.080 --> 39:14.160
-You smiled first.
-No, you smiled first.

39:14.240 --> 39:16.440
-You did first.
-You did first.

39:20.040 --> 39:20.960
I did first.

39:35.240 --> 39:37.240
If you make me fall, you're dead.

39:37.320 --> 39:39.040
‎-Bravo!
‎-Bravo!

39:43.720 --> 39:45.720
‎-Congratulations!
‎-Be happy together!

39:49.080 --> 39:50.920
By Sacred Heaven above,

39:51.520 --> 39:53.800
first bow to heaven and earth!

40:02.120 --> 40:03.800
-With the ancestors as witness…
-Wonderful!

40:03.880 --> 40:05.280
Second bow to your kin!

40:14.200 --> 40:15.720
Let the holy mountain bear witness

40:16.400 --> 40:18.000
and the sacred waters seal your vow.

40:18.080 --> 40:20.760
Third bow to each other!

40:29.080 --> 40:30.240
I'm fine.

40:31.760 --> 40:33.920
Ceremony complete.

40:34.000 --> 40:35.160
Now kiss!

41:33.400 --> 41:34.440
Di Zhu,

41:35.480 --> 41:36.680
here's the Star Stone.

41:40.600 --> 41:41.440
Come out, Little Nine.

42:03.000 --> 42:05.200
Hold your breath.
There's sleeping powder in the sandstorm.

42:47.960 --> 42:48.920
The Star Stone.
